      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good overall condition and has been well-maintained throughout its life. The engine is strong and reliable, and the interior is clean with only minor wear consistent with careful use. While the exterior paint still holds a great shine, you may find a few small stone chips or light surface scratches upon close inspection. It drives smoothly and is ready for its next owner to enjoy immediately without any urgent repairs needed.",
