    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presented in impeccable showroom condition, this vehicle represents the pinnacle of automotive preservation. Every detail, from the flawless exterior finish to the pristine interior appointments, reflects a standard of care synonymous with investment-grade quality. Meticulously maintained and mechanically absolute, this specimen offers an unrivaled experience for the discerning collector who demands nothing less than perfection.",
