    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "This E92 M3 is a superlative example of the high-revving S65 4.0L V8 platform. The engine exhibits optimal oil pressure and precise throttle response via its individual throttle bodies. The 6-speed manual gearbox offers short, positive throws, coupled with a pristine clutch engagement. Mechanically, the vehicle is bolstered by proactive rod bearing replacement and upgraded throttle actuators, mitigating common platform weak points. The chassis integrity is absolute, featuring a carbon-fiber roof for a lower center of gravity and a perfectly preserved suspension assembly. Finished in Alpine White over Novillo leather, the interior maintains its factory tactile feel with zero bolster wear. This is a turn-key, collector-grade vehicle for the discerning purist.",
